Warning:
Fauna is decommissioning FQL v4 on June 30, 2025.

This driver is not compatible with FQL v10, the latest version. Fauna accounts created after August 21, 2024 must use FQL v10.
Ensure you migrate existing projects to the official v10 driver by the v4 EOL date: https://github.com/fauna/fauna-jvm.

For more information, see the v4 end of life (EOL) announcement and related FAQ.

com.faunadb.client.util

Class SymbolGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.faunadb.client.util.SymbolGenerator

  • public final class SymbolGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    The singleton SymbolGenerator is used to automatically generate symbol names when a Java lambda function is provided where a FaunaDB lambda expression is accepted. The symbol space is 2^64 and thread-safe.
